value.string: To Unlock the policy in Horison Unlock application
Launch the HomeSite DBA Admin Tools application
Navigate to Unlock Horison Policy screen
Select the Horison Environment and Enter Lock UserID and Policy /Quote Number and Click on Execute Procedure
In case of failure while Loading the file/entering to a field, ERROR flag will be raised and BOT may be stopped
